One year ago, we put a ring on forever… and yesterday, we quietly celebrated that promise — just us, some pizza, flowers, and the cutest cake. 💍🍕🌸

With this handsome, kind and truly wonderful man by my side, even the simplest evenings feel like magic. ✨

Can’t believe it’s already been a whole year since we said “yes” to forever — and honestly, I’d choose this calm, cozy kind of love a thousand times over. ❤️

Here’s to more memories, more laughter, and more pizza nights with you @kanishq.dwivedi 🤍
Love you more than you know ❤️😘

They say the best kind of love feels like home... and in every corner of this beautiful island, I found mine in you @kanishq.dwivedi ❤️

The way you look at me, the way we laugh together—it’s the kind of forever I always dreamed of.
Even surrounded by all this beauty, it was your presence that made every second feel full... real... and unforgettable. 🌊🐚

This was hands down one of the most beautiful mornings of my life 🌅🤍

Woke up in our beach villa at @heritanceaarah in the Maldives, pulled the sheets off, and this is what I saw... ocean 🌊 right in front of me, the sound of waves hitting the shore, curtains flowing with the breeze, and the sun slowly rising over the horizon 🏝️🌞✨. 

The view, the vibe, the calm... unmatched 😇. 

Is this on your bucket list too? 🤍 Let me know!
